10000
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="info"

Test product information
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Detailed description of the test product
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
